entities.name: ElizaOS
entities.description: A development framework with a focus on improving core architecture, bug fixes, and plugin system restructuring. It allows for 'scripting behavior' beyond scheduling posts and features agent-managed DAOs.

entities.name: Shaw
entities.description: A key team member involved in the development of ElizaOS. He temporarily stepped away from Twitter.

entities.name: Twitter
entities.description: A social media platform for microblogging and social networking. Formerly known as X.

entities.name: PrinceSCRT

entities.name: Secret Network
entities.description: A community that launched the PrinceSCRT token on the auto.fun platform.

entities.name: ElizaOS v2

entities.name: Jin

entities.name: DOOD

entities.name: GitHub
entities.description: A web-based platform for version control and collaboration, primarily used for software development. It hosts projects and facilitates contributions.

entities.name: Groq
